install_msg:
Thank you for installing the Collectable cog!
This cog allows your guild members to buy collectables, and is just meant as a way to have fun on your guild
description: A mini game based around Red's economy system, this cog allows people in servers to buy Collectables and display them. It would be good to have a cog loaded that affects a user's bank balance.
end_user_data_statement: This cog doesn't store any data on anyone, don't worry :D
